{"tid":1988536,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"合建P4實驗室 華逼走法專家","createTime":"2020-04-25T09:25:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-25T10:47:07.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b02adf3bef3ab47605d2963841ab441f79d1137c","tid":1988536,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T09:25:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200425/Z4IXTIOJEIBJ5I45DPL5UYLGAM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200425%2FZ4IXTIOJEIBJ5I45DPL5UYLGAM%2F&d=5PHCsmqc8bXRSfVPwy6hKq%2BFBM5c0LZ9Ts2TrilmEa4%3D&h=e1da1dc3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200425%2FZ4IXTIOJEIBJ5I45DPL5UYLGAM%2F&h=6dace3dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200425/Z4IXTIOJEIBJ5I45DPL5UYLGAM/</a><br />\n<br />\n合建P4實驗室 華逼走法專家<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200425/large/1587743481_3294.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200425%2Flarge%2F1587743481_3294.gif&h=409c6992&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中法合建武漢P4實驗室，建成後被中共佔據。<br />\n<br />\n經歷武漢肺炎爆發後，湖北省發改委前天在一天內，批准武漢華中科技大學總投資逾100億元人民幣（約109億港元）的十個項目，全部與應對突發公共衞生事件的能力有關，包括應急防控P3實驗室及檢測中心、在該校的同濟醫院建立重大突發公共衞生事件疑難危急重症救治中心，和在協和醫院建立國家區域重大疫情防控基地。法媒指，有傳是病毒來源的武漢病毒研究院P4實驗室，是法國協助建立，但後來中方將法方邊緣化並控制實驗室。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：五萬人後日考通識「高危」<br />\n<br />\n沙士後合作<br />\n<br />\n法廣網的調查報道指，武漢P4實驗室在2003年沙士肆虐後，法國時任總統希拉克決定與中國共建。實驗室在2010年動工，2015年建成，2018年1月啟用。可是，中方公司主導按規格建造的大部份P4實驗室，僅密閉隔離空間佈置的特定技術和知識才是法國掌握。中方對法專家處處提防、排斥，令法國專家失望，想停工卻不能。<br />\n<br />\n最後法專家離任雙邊委員會主席，原計劃到華的50名法國專家亦沒出發，實驗室完全落入中國控制，合作名存實亡。法專家批評「P4（實驗室）是一種非常中國化的工具」，即使是有法國的技術協助「它也屬於中國」。曾任雙邊委員會主席的法公共衞生專家梅瑞爾（Alain Merieux）承認，2006年以來中法兩個傳染病委員會從未召開會議，武漢P4實驗室只有中國研究員工作。<br />\n<br />\n澎湃新聞網/法廣網"},{"pid":"74e12f039bec88ecbb624b492de2cef0ac36013e","tid":1988536,"uid":49588,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T09:36:51.000Z","msg":"法國人真係好戇居<br />\n<br />\nP4實驗室<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n核電廠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30a85624d19ec1bc1b708db03356271fe430f6e0","tid":1988536,"uid":252069,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T09:40:09.000Z","msg":"that's why 法國個諾貝爾得獎者出來講野<br />\n佢仲要話好熟悉間P4實驗室<br />\n<br />\nBTW,<br />\n(重開)香港社會運動需要轉型<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1988467\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1988467</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ixjbr30.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fixjbr30.jpg&h=3dd23a07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UuJC633.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUuJC633.jpg&h=bd20a436&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d1086fbbe95b36c9a319feb244e1e0c7cacffbcf","tid":1988536,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T10:39:18.000Z","msg":"法媒：武漢P4實驗室初由中法共建 後被中國據為己有<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=388866&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D388866%26refer%3DShare&d=5PHCsmqc8bXRSfVPwy6hKq%2BFBM5c0LZ9Ts2TrilmEa4%3D&h=f679e38b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D388866%26refer%3DShare&h=793b4760\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=388866&amp;refer=Share</a>"},{"pid":"d8b618f30582b57647be3e6e1ae